dubstep.solution.plan

Class Limit

  • java.lang.Object
    • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator
      • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator.Unary
        • dubstep.solution.plan.Limit

  • public class Limit
extends Operator.Unary
    A concrete implementation of a relational plan operator representing a limit operator. Supports offset clauses as well as limit clauses.
